Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.the_tarlords.data.event.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class Event extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable
This class represents an event has name, location, start and end date and time poster, organizer and QR codes related to it
